38:02.280 --> 38:05.408
And God help me, the one thing I
do understand, Sonny, is football.

38:05.409 --> 38:06.950
That's me.

38:06.951 --> 38:10.546
I'm action-oriented.
I'm passionate.

38:10.622 --> 38:14.217
I'm a Cleveland girl,
and I am football.

