38:51.246 --> 38:53.997
Anyway, he got really mad and
started throwing stuff around,

38:53.998 --> 38:56.751
and then he said he was gonna
go down to the locker room.

38:56.835 --> 39:00.420
After all that rehab, you're just gonna
quit? You're just gonna walk away?

39:00.421 --> 39:01.922
C'mon, Brian. Don't listen
to Coach. Don't leave.

39:01.923 --> 39:03.090
I know what's goin' on here.

39:03.091 --> 39:05.685
Then just compete with him!
Beat him out!

39:14.102 --> 39:15.435
Did you trash my office?

39:15.436 --> 39:16.770
Trade me.

39:16.771 --> 39:18.814
Did you just trash my office?

39:18.815 --> 39:20.983
Yeah. I'm upset.

39:20.984 --> 39:22.150
Well, I don't care if you're upset.

39:22.151 --> 39:23.944
If you're upset, call
your agent, all right?

39:23.945 --> 39:26.154
Let him have this conversation.
That's what he's there for.

39:26.155 --> 39:28.657
No, Sonny. You're gonna talk to me.
Man-to-man. You owe me that.

39:28.658 --> 39:29.992
I owe you?

39:29.993 --> 39:31.118
I drafted you.

39:31.119 --> 39:32.578
Your dad drafted me.

39:32.579 --> 39:34.456
No, Drew, I drafted you.

39:35.039 --> 39:37.541
I may have been in San Francisco,

39:37.542 --> 39:40.670
but my dad wasn't even looking
at you until I told him to.

39:40.962 --> 39:44.298
Yeah, and when your knee crapped
out and no one wanted you,

39:44.299 --> 39:45.591
I still extended your contract,

39:45.592 --> 39:46.800
and I think I even
gave you a raise,

39:46.801 --> 39:48.518
because I believed in you.

39:48.636 --> 39:50.729
Then why pick Callahan?

39:51.222 --> 39:53.019
You know why.

39:53.558 --> 39:55.651
Then trade me.

39:57.312 --> 39:59.980
I'm gonna do what's
best for the team.

39:59.981 --> 40:03.901
I've been in this league for eight
seasons. I've been to the playoffs.

40:03.902 --> 40:06.904
I know the system that Penn wants to
run and I know I can make it work.

40:06.905 --> 40:10.657
I've busted my ass this off-season.
I set the bar high.

40:10.658 --> 40:14.002
I'm in great shape.
I feel 10 years younger.

40:14.245 --> 40:16.705
I'm tellin' you,
man, I swear to you,

40:16.706 --> 40:20.050
the best thing for this
team, this season, is me.

40:20.501 --> 40:21.919
Are you finished?

40:21.920 --> 40:23.421
No.

40:23.504 --> 40:25.221
Well, get finished.

40:25.673 --> 40:27.674
And then get back to work.

40:27.675 --> 40:31.178
If I trade you, I trade you.
And if I don't, I don't.

40:31.179 --> 40:34.681
Do yourself a favor. Worry about
Brian. Don't worry about Bo.

40:34.682 --> 40:37.559
And definitely, most absolutely
goddamn importantly,

40:37.560 --> 40:39.853
