41:56.180 --> 41:57.932
<i>Hey, Pete. What's up?</i>

41:57.974 --> 42:00.100
Well, we're in the market for a QB,

42:00.101 --> 42:02.185
and now that you have number one,

42:02.186 --> 42:04.939
I was wondering if Brian
Drew's available.

42:05.440 --> 42:07.649
I don't know. Haven't
made up my mind yet.

42:07.650 --> 42:09.109
