42:20.288 --> 42:22.122
We like what we see.

42:22.123 --> 42:24.624
He did? That's great.

42:24.625 --> 42:26.843
You seem surprised.

42:28.296 --> 42:31.140
Why would I be surprised?

42:31.632 --> 42:34.384
Okay, Sonny. You don't have
